snippet.title: Infinite Library Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Trailer for Infinite Library, by DarkStorm Interactive. Releases 4/29/2024

Become the Librarian, Alex!
You are Alex, the Librarian of the expansive Infinite Library! Wavedash, Wall Jump, and navigate through treacherous puzzles using the platforming abilities of Books of Power to vanquish The Corruption.
